{"tid":2323121,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"區域法院一名後勤支援人員確診新型肺炎","createTime":"2020-12-13T02:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T02:25:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c51c24e7f7e0ff7d222c9cb6997c1b285eb63708","tid":2323121,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T02:25:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565014-20201213.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565014-20201213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mQjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=b64c91b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565014-20201213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=724d6f3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565014-20201213.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n區域法院一名後勤支援人員確診感染新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n司法機構表示，該名員工本月9日因身體不適求診，昨晚確診，最近一次返回法院上班日為本月7日，她的工作不需要接觸法庭使用者。<br />\n<br />\n司法機構指，已清潔消毒法院內相關辦公室及公眾地方，目前並無接獲衞生防護中心通知，有任何員工或其他人士被列為相關密切接觸者。"}]}